<h2 class="text-headline-md font-headline-md text-on-surface mb-stack-md">Core Soil Health Principles</h2>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
<div class="md:col-span-2 bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-6">
<div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary-container text-on-primary-container flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[32px]" data-icon="science">science</span>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="text-title-lg font-title-lg text-primary mb-1">Pre-Sowing Soil Testing</h4>
<p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Measure pH and available nutrients. Farmers save an average of ₹2,500/acre by eliminating unnecessary applications.</p>
<a class="inline-block mt-2 text-primary font-label-md hover:underline" href="#">Map of nearest KVK Labs →</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="bg-secondary-container/20 border-2 border-secondary-container p-6 rounded-xl flex flex-col justify-between">
<h4 class="text-title-lg font-title-lg text-secondary mb-2">Nitrogen Fixation</h4>
<p class="text-caption text-on-surface-variant">Integrating legumes in your rotation can naturally add up to 30-40kg of Nitrogen per hectare.</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant shadow-sm flex flex-col">
<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" data-icon="compost">compost</span>
<h4 class="text-label-md font-bold text-primary">Organic Enrichment</h4>
</div>
<p class="text-caption text-on-surface-variant">Use FYM (Farm Yard Manure) to enhance the Cation Exchange Capacity (CEC) of your soil.</p>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-2 bg-primary text-on-primary p-6 rounded-xl border border-primary flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-center">
<div class="w-full md:w-2/3">
<h4 class="text-title-lg font-title-lg mb-1">Erosion Control Strategy</h4>
<p class="text-body-md opacity-90">Implement mulching and contour bunding. Preserving topsoil prevents nutrient washout during heavy monsoon rains.</p>
</div>
<div class="w-full md:w-1/3 flex justify-end">
<button class="px-6 py-2 bg-white text-primary font-label-md rounded-full shadow-lg">Learn Techniques</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
